    "content": "# Arkhe Sentiment Engine\n\n## Beginner Level\n\n### What Is It?\nThe Arkhe Sentiment Engine is the multi-source system that quantifies market psychology and narrative formation.\n\n### Origin\nBuilt as the behavioral intelligence layer of Arkhe.\n\n### Why It Matters\nSentiment often leads price and provides early warning of regime shifts.\n\n## Intermediate Level\n\n### Market Mechanics\nEngine processes news, social, and on-chain data for tone and narrative velocity.\n\n### How It Behaves\nSentiment Engine detects euphoria and panic before they become obvious in price.\n\n### Key Data to Watch\n- Sentiment velocity and uniformity\n\n## Advanced Level\n\n### Institutional Behavior\nArkhe Sentiment Engine feeds contrarian and tactical signals.\n\n### Professional Use Cases\n- Narrative-driven positioning\n\n### AI Interpretation in Systems Like Arkhe\n- **Sentiment Agent**: Core engine for all behavioral analysis.\n\n### Key Takeaways\nThe Arkhe Sentiment Engine quantifies the market’s emotional state.\n\n## Related Topics\n- arkhe_macro_engine.md\n"
